.../tenants/tenant-name/availableServicePlans

Data type

Method

Use

Access

Notes

List

GET

Retrieve a list of the service plans that are available for the tenant to assign to its namespaces

For an HCP tenant, tenant-level user account with the monitor or administrator role For the default tenant, system-level user account with the monitor or administrator role

Valid only if the tenant is configured to allow service plan selection.

The listed service plans are identified by service plan name.

In XML, each listed service plan is the value of an element named name. In JSON, the name in the name/value pair that lists the service plans is nam e. .../tenants/tenant-name/availableServicePlans/service-plan-name

